name: Planet GS Red Jasper
description: Planet GS Red Jasper is the planet of powerful physical and spiritual protection. This planet helps ground you as it represents the root chakra. Here you are helped to act on your passions. This planet energizes you and helps you feel joy and positivity. It is here that you should find motivation, inspiration and energy to reach your full potential. This planet includes LED changing colored lights, and it glows differently under UV light, regular light, and no light.
